s the virtues of hard work, honesty, and fairness."],"variants":[]},{"name":"de","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["Pet form of any of the given names beginning with the letter <i>D-</i> (  compare  Jay   and   Kay  ), in particular   Dorothy .  It is also used as an independent name, and may in some cases be associated with the River Dee (  compare  Clyde  )."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs Piers de Bassingham was born about 1162, in England, United Kingdom. She had at least 4 daughters with Piers De Bassingham."},"et":{"about 1162–":"umbes 1162–Surnud","1160–Male":"1160–Surnud","1165–Female":"1165–Surnud","1170–Female":"1170–Surnud","1172–Female":"1172–Surnud","1189–Female":"1189–Surnud","1162–Female":"1162–Surnud","about 1162":"umbes 1162","1189":"1189","Abt 1187":"umbes 1172","1165":"1165","1162":"1162","about 1165":"umbes 1165","1172":"1172","Abt 1170":"umbes 1170","1160":"1160","1170":"1170","of Norfolk, England, United Kingdom":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom",",,, England, United Kingdom":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England, United Kingdom":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom","East Dereham, Norfolk, England":"Dereham, Norfolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1162–":"noin 1162–Kuollut","1160–Male":"1160–Kuollut","1165–Female":"1165–Kuollut","1170–Female":"1170–Kuollut","1172–Female":"1172–Kuollut","1189–Female":"1189–Kuollut","1162–Female":"1162–Kuollut","about 1162":"noin 1162","1189":"1189","Abt 1187":"noin 1172","1165":"1165","1162":"1162","about 1165":"noin 1165","1172":"1172","Abt 1170":"noin 1170","1160":"1160","1170":"1170","of Norfolk, England, United Kingdom":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta",",,, England, United Kingdom":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England, United Kingdom":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","East Dereham, Norfolk, England":"Dereham, Norfolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1162–":"environ 1162–Décédée","1160–Male